ygData.messageBody:
Not really a POS, my level 41 rogue switches it out to backstab with...hit for 170 twice tonight with the thing, and thats not even close to max with that weapon, which is alreay far above my SBD which maxed at 160 unbuffed. Its good to have played a bard, makes weapon switching much more realistic :) *wishes she had a crystilline spear* Mmm...300+dmg backstabs....

Ueni Murisan, 41st rogue of Tunare
